{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564210/extras/forttop.gif?t=1728241425\" />Fort Craft is a simulation game in which you conquer and manage forts and also fight battles. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take part in the siege, then make the reconstruction, and be prepared for defense of your fortification.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Become Fortification Master ! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Repair walls, build reinforced cannon posts, rearrange fort for your needs</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564210/extras/shoot.gif?t=1728241425\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Rebuild the Fort</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gather required materials, make plans and stay prepared</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564210/extras/wall.gif?t=1728241425\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Conquer and win campaigns on tactical map ! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use the best tactics and combined arms to win battles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564210/extras/map.gif?t=1728241425\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Discover and Conquer new territories !</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Try out 3 different campaigns all around the world</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564210/extras/build.gif?t=1728241425\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Build new better cannons, prepare your fort for the worst ! </h2><p class=